@startuml
title PowGo Protected Resource Access Flow

actor Client as C
participant "PowGo" as P
participant "Upstream Server" as U

== Initial Request (No Puzzle) ==

C -> P: Request protected resource\n(without puzzle solution)
note right of C: No nonce/solution attached

P --> C: Status Code 299 (Warning)\nPuzzle: "Find nonce that makes\nSHA256 hash start with specific pattern"
note right of P: Challenge includes data & pattern

== Client Solves Puzzle ==

C -> C: Find nonce via brute force\n(computational work)

== Retry with Solution ==

C -> P: Retry original request\n+ solution (nonce attached)

P -> P: Verify nonce solution\nCheck SHA256 pattern match

P -> P: Cache valid nonce\n(short time window)

P -> U: Proxy request upstream\n(with original content)

U --> P: Upstream response

P --> C: Return response to client

@enduml
